WEBVTT

01:44.140 --> 01:48.910
[A LOVER IN THE MORTAL WORLD]

01:49.590 --> 01:51.539
[Episode 1]

01:55.390 --> 01:56.590
Eight years ago,

01:57.120 --> 01:59.120
a plague swept through the capital,

01:59.310 --> 02:01.110
causing countless casualties.

02:01.560 --> 02:04.020
Han Changsong, Deputy Director
of the Imperial Medical Academy,

02:04.020 --> 02:05.570
was falsely accused of treason

02:05.570 --> 02:07.660
because of a single prescription.

02:08.150 --> 02:09.680
Overnight,

02:10.030 --> 02:11.830
his entire family was executed.

02:16.840 --> 02:18.520
Sister!

02:21.960 --> 02:25.560
By the mandate of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees:

02:26.030 --> 02:28.520
Han Changsong, Deputy Director
of the Imperial Medical Academy,

02:28.520 --> 02:30.360
under the guise of saving lives,

02:30.360 --> 02:32.680
has murdered over ten thousand
soldiers and civilians.

02:32.680 --> 02:34.150
His crime warrants death.

02:34.800 --> 02:36.470
Now the evidence is clear,

02:36.470 --> 02:38.590
and his crimes are beyond forgiveness.

02:38.590 --> 02:40.079
The entire Han family

02:40.150 --> 02:43.030
shall be exterminated to the third generation,
their ancestral hall razed,

02:43.030 --> 02:46.400
their medical texts burned, and their
healing lineage extinguished forever.

02:46.400 --> 02:48.150
So decreed!

02:48.710 --> 02:50.470
Let me out!

02:51.400 --> 02:53.079
Let me out!

03:17.400 --> 03:18.030
Ling.

03:18.800 --> 03:19.680
Hold on.

03:20.240 --> 03:21.590
You must hold on.

03:22.190 --> 03:24.590
The Han family bloodline
cannot be cut off—

03:24.760 --> 03:26.130
never!

03:42.720 --> 03:43.510
Mo.

03:43.980 --> 03:45.910
I will definitely come to save you.

03:59.750 --> 04:00.710
I've never seen a bride

04:00.710 --> 04:02.490
throw herself at the groom like this.

04:02.490 --> 04:03.770
What else can I do?

04:04.080 --> 04:06.470
To reach the Jinglan capital
as soon as possible,

04:06.470 --> 04:08.870
marrying the Jinglan envoy
is the only way.

04:15.120 --> 04:15.920
We were living

04:16.310 --> 04:17.510
just fine in Changmo.

04:17.510 --> 04:19.040
Why rush back to Jinglan?

04:19.060 --> 04:21.060
I have to go back and save my brother.

04:21.310 --> 04:22.070
Han Mo?

04:22.560 --> 04:23.310
Didn't your second uncle say

04:23.310 --> 04:24.560
he was already dead?

04:35.560 --> 04:36.190
Alright.

04:36.510 --> 04:37.310
Go back now

04:37.870 --> 04:39.409
and tell my second uncle that

04:39.409 --> 04:41.810
I'll make it safely
to the Jinglan Capital.

04:51.290 --> 04:52.730
You useless Xiao Chi,

04:53.159 --> 04:55.050
come down here!

05:21.950 --> 05:22.660
Come on.

05:22.680 --> 05:23.360
Xiao Chi.

05:23.720 --> 05:25.750
I'd like to see just how capable

05:26.160 --> 05:29.160
this so-called God of Slaughter
of Jinglan really is!

06:28.280 --> 06:29.050
Wait.

06:32.320 --> 06:33.880
You are truly skilled.

06:34.080 --> 06:35.760
I knew you had an old injury.

06:35.790 --> 06:37.310
Now it's been triggered

06:37.360 --> 06:38.690
by the force of my blade.

06:39.370 --> 06:41.270
At this point, even if I defeat you,

06:41.270 --> 06:42.930
it would be an unfair victory.

06:43.240 --> 06:44.120
You people of Changmo

06:44.120 --> 06:45.560
still care about martial virtue?

06:45.560 --> 06:46.360
No more words.

06:46.520 --> 06:46.980
Come on.

06:47.260 --> 06:48.040
Let's fight again!

06:48.040 --> 06:49.560
I came today for two reasons.

06:49.560 --> 06:50.310
First, to see whether your title

06:50.310 --> 06:52.770
as the "God of Slaughter"
is deserved or not.

06:52.920 --> 06:54.780
Second, I have something for you.

06:58.330 --> 06:59.250
In seven days,

06:59.440 --> 07:02.000
the marriage delegation
from Changmo will arrive.

07:02.000 --> 07:03.680
When your envoy comes,

07:03.920 --> 07:04.950
give this to him.

07:05.870 --> 07:08.430
We Changmo people
are not unable to defeat you,

07:08.430 --> 07:10.610
we just don't want to hurt the innocent.

07:10.610 --> 07:12.390
Otherwise, our Changmo valiant cavalry

07:12.390 --> 07:13.990
will flatten Tianlang Pass.

07:13.990 --> 07:14.790
In that case,

07:15.200 --> 07:16.490
please go back

07:16.510 --> 07:17.710
and tell your Emperor

07:18.080 --> 07:20.080
to cherish this marriage alliance,

07:20.080 --> 07:22.630
so that our two nations
may remain friends forever,

07:22.630 --> 07:24.030
and never again go to war.

07:24.920 --> 07:26.160
We won!

07:26.190 --> 07:28.400
General Xiao has returned
victorious again!

07:28.400 --> 07:29.400
We won!

07:29.600 --> 07:32.130
General Xiao has returned
victorious again!

07:32.310 --> 07:33.390
We won!

07:33.390 --> 07:36.070
General Xiao has returned
victorious again!

07:36.310 --> 07:37.630
We won!

07:37.630 --> 07:40.270
General Xiao has returned
victorious again!

07:41.060 --> 07:41.860
General Xiao.

07:41.950 --> 07:44.720
General Xiao.

07:45.040 --> 07:45.840
General Xiao.

07:46.040 --> 07:48.560
General Xiao.

07:48.870 --> 07:49.870
General Xiao.

07:50.120 --> 07:52.830
General Xiao.

07:54.270 --> 07:57.159
General Xiao.

08:10.730 --> 08:13.760
Why would Changmo suddenly
propose a marriage alliance?

08:13.760 --> 08:14.690
What do you think

08:15.310 --> 08:16.570
they're really after?

08:17.260 --> 08:18.600
Your Majesty, please rest assured.

08:18.600 --> 08:19.440
Now that I am going,

08:19.440 --> 08:21.500
I will definitely find out the truth.

08:22.690 --> 08:23.210
Huo Ran.

08:24.480 --> 08:25.070
Huo Ran.

08:29.070 --> 08:29.590
My lord.

08:30.800 --> 08:33.200
How many days
until we reach Tianlang Pass?

08:33.549 --> 08:34.360
At this speed,

08:34.549 --> 08:35.520
we should arrive

08:35.549 --> 08:36.669
in about five days.

08:37.080 --> 08:37.610
Too slow.

08:37.940 --> 08:39.390
Tell everyone to speed up.

08:39.390 --> 08:41.590
We must reach Tianlang Pass
within three days.

08:41.590 --> 08:42.039
Yes.

08:44.120 --> 08:45.830
Everyone, full speed ahead!

08:46.080 --> 08:48.680
We must reach Tianlang Pass
within three days.

08:49.680 --> 08:51.290
[General's Mansion]

08:49.910 --> 08:50.760
Congratulations, General.

08:50.760 --> 08:52.960
The victory report has been submitted.

08:53.080 --> 08:54.630
General Xiao is naturally invincible.

08:54.630 --> 08:55.030
Right.

08:55.800 --> 08:57.200
I'm only worried that
this Governor Zhao Gao

08:57.200 --> 08:58.400
is a troublesome man.

09:02.270 --> 09:02.870
General.

09:04.270 --> 09:05.480
Lord Zhao sent an invitation.

09:05.480 --> 09:06.830
He says he will hold his wedding tonight

09:06.830 --> 09:08.220
and invites us to attend.

09:08.220 --> 09:09.100
[To General Xiao Chi:
The Zhao family
confirms the marriage alliance.]

09:09.130 --> 09:09.860
[A wedding banquet will be held tonight.
You are respectfully invited.]

09:15.270 --> 09:17.010
I've never seen a bride
offer herself up like this before.

09:17.010 --> 09:18.010
How strange.

09:18.040 --> 09:20.500
That woman's been crying
to marry Lord Zhao.

09:20.600 --> 09:21.400
Does she think

09:21.510 --> 09:23.840
marrying up will make her a phoenix?

09:24.000 --> 09:24.760
Exactly.

09:25.280 --> 09:26.440
What is she even thinking?

09:26.440 --> 09:28.510
My beauty… where is my beauty?

09:28.830 --> 09:29.390
Ms. Wu.

09:30.250 --> 09:31.200
Lord Zhao.

09:31.750 --> 09:33.670
Where is my Changmo beauty?

09:34.280 --> 09:35.850
She's been here for quite a while.

09:35.850 --> 09:37.410
I've already dressed her
in the wedding gown.

09:37.410 --> 09:38.380
She is just waiting

09:38.380 --> 09:40.710
to perform the wedding ceremony with you.

09:41.280 --> 09:42.090
Lord Zhao.

09:42.120 --> 09:43.490
The ceremony is about to start.

09:43.490 --> 09:45.020
What are you doing here now?

09:45.120 --> 09:46.790
I just came to check

09:48.200 --> 09:49.600
so I can pay you properly.

09:49.770 --> 09:51.200
Out of the way, move.

10:08.480 --> 10:09.290
Good.

10:11.000 --> 10:12.200
Good.

10:13.550 --> 10:14.630
Take your money

10:15.930 --> 10:16.590
and get out.

10:23.470 --> 10:26.620
I never knew Changmo had such a beauty.

10:27.200 --> 10:27.660
Come on,

10:28.080 --> 10:28.870
say something

10:28.870 --> 10:29.510
for me.

10:31.080 --> 10:32.150
Lord Zhao.

10:33.910 --> 10:34.910
Good… good.

10:35.160 --> 10:36.560
Then I'd like to see

10:36.970 --> 10:38.830
how well you serve a man.

10:39.630 --> 10:40.690
What are you doing?

10:44.090 --> 10:45.310
You don't understand.

10:45.310 --> 10:46.520
We Changmo women

10:46.550 --> 10:47.810
are taught from a young age

10:47.810 --> 10:50.380
to obey our husbands completely.

10:50.840 --> 10:52.640
Whatever our husbands request,

10:52.910 --> 10:54.150
we will fulfill.

10:55.480 --> 10:57.240
Then why are you stopping me?

10:57.320 --> 10:58.120
Hurry up, come serve me.

10:58.120 --> 10:58.670
But

10:59.630 --> 11:02.040
we only obey

11:02.680 --> 11:03.800
our own husbands.

11:04.180 --> 11:06.540
I am your husband.

11:06.730 --> 11:07.680
Come on.

11:07.790 --> 11:09.390
-Take your clothes off.
-No.

11:10.000 --> 11:12.120
We haven't held the wedding ceremony yet.

11:12.120 --> 11:13.850
We're not officially married.

11:13.870 --> 11:15.270
This is not Changmo,

11:15.270 --> 11:16.320
there are no such rules here.

11:16.320 --> 11:16.840
Come.

11:16.840 --> 11:18.720
There is another legend in Changmo.

11:18.720 --> 11:20.050
If a woman has intimate contact

11:20.050 --> 11:22.050
with a man before marriage,

11:22.120 --> 11:23.950
that man will be cursed with misfortune

11:23.950 --> 11:26.070
and soon suffer divine retribution.

11:27.640 --> 11:28.970
What legend?

11:29.240 --> 11:30.000
I don't care.

11:30.000 --> 11:30.720
Lord Zhao.

11:35.330 --> 11:37.060
Have you thought this through?

11:48.080 --> 11:48.680
Forget it.

11:49.330 --> 11:50.750
I'll wait until after

11:51.080 --> 11:51.960
the wedding ceremony

11:51.960 --> 11:52.760
is completed.

11:52.960 --> 11:53.520
Alright.

11:56.650 --> 11:57.550
Wait for me.

12:01.060 --> 12:03.460
A fated match at Tianlang Pass,

12:03.490 --> 12:05.920
with spring breezes full of tenderness.

12:06.150 --> 12:08.480
I'd like to ask
on behalf of everyone here.

12:08.600 --> 12:11.630
Are you truly in love?

12:11.630 --> 12:13.840
I share deep feelings with my beauty.

12:13.960 --> 12:15.670
Of course we are in love.

12:15.780 --> 12:17.150
Then Lord Zhao,

12:17.170 --> 12:18.170
please share

12:18.200 --> 12:19.880
your story with everyone.

12:20.270 --> 12:21.270
Right.

12:21.290 --> 12:22.900
Tell us.

12:26.170 --> 12:27.690
Well, we...

12:29.750 --> 12:31.030
we...

12:32.070 --> 12:33.800
Enough with all this nonsense!

12:34.080 --> 12:35.360
I am a third-rank official,

12:35.360 --> 12:36.610
taking a frontier woman as a concubine.

12:36.610 --> 12:37.640
I have to pay for the banquet,

12:37.640 --> 12:39.140
follow all the wedding rituals,

12:39.140 --> 12:41.240
and still tell stories
to entertain you all?

12:41.240 --> 12:42.480
Hurry up.

12:42.620 --> 12:43.390
Drink if you want to drink,

12:43.390 --> 12:44.240
and do whatever you want.

12:44.240 --> 12:44.790
Don't waste my time with my beauty.

12:44.790 --> 12:46.250
General Xiao has arrived!

12:46.710 --> 12:47.510
General Xiao.

12:47.960 --> 12:48.730
Lord Zhao.

12:49.150 --> 12:50.550
How could I possibly miss

12:50.750 --> 12:52.030
your big day?

12:52.050 --> 12:53.290
General Xiao.

12:53.980 --> 12:55.220
You came just in time.

12:55.250 --> 12:56.110
Serve the wine.

12:56.170 --> 12:57.970
Let me toast General Xiao first.

12:58.240 --> 12:59.120
I'm not here

12:59.510 --> 13:01.000
for your wedding wine.

13:03.630 --> 13:04.290
Chengfeng.

13:04.650 --> 13:05.950
Tell him why I'm here.

13:06.240 --> 13:06.840
Lord Zhao.

13:07.150 --> 13:10.670
You embezzled 800,000 taels of
military funds and provisions.

13:10.670 --> 13:11.790
800,000 taels?

13:12.240 --> 13:13.090
That much?

13:13.110 --> 13:13.830
Seriously?

13:15.490 --> 13:16.400
Xiao Chi.

13:17.200 --> 13:19.000
How dare you investigate me in secret.

13:19.000 --> 13:20.900
I wouldn't have known
without investigating—

13:20.900 --> 13:22.030
but after checking,

13:22.040 --> 13:22.710
Lord Zhao,

13:23.240 --> 13:24.520
you're truly corrupt.

13:24.540 --> 13:25.020
You...

13:25.870 --> 13:26.550
Chengfeng.

13:27.600 --> 13:28.080
Guards,

13:28.270 --> 13:28.870
take him away.

13:28.870 --> 13:29.320
Yes.

13:29.630 --> 13:30.480
Don't move! Don't move!

13:30.480 --> 13:31.480
It hurts!

13:32.630 --> 13:33.430
General Xiao.

13:33.630 --> 13:35.000
My uncle is the minister of the court,

13:35.000 --> 13:35.930
Lord Wang Ruhai.

13:36.160 --> 13:37.800
I'm from an official family.

13:38.150 --> 13:40.200
Show me some mercy—

13:40.720 --> 13:41.850
for my uncle's sake.

13:41.880 --> 13:43.550
General Xiao rules with strict discipline.

13:43.550 --> 13:44.810
How could he spare you?

13:45.030 --> 13:45.830
Take him away!

13:46.150 --> 13:47.030
Xiao Chi!

13:47.390 --> 13:48.690
-You're abusing military power!
-Hurry up!

13:48.690 --> 13:49.950
You are slandering me!

13:49.970 --> 13:51.260
I will tell my uncle!

13:51.290 --> 13:51.750
Cut the crap.

13:51.750 --> 13:52.360
-Let go of me!
-Hurry up!

13:52.360 --> 13:53.120
Let me go!

13:54.320 --> 13:54.840
What,

13:55.330 --> 13:57.890
still staying for the wedding wine?

14:09.510 --> 14:10.240
Miss.

14:11.320 --> 14:12.450
Aren't you leaving?

14:12.600 --> 14:14.680
Still planning to marry Zhao Gao?

14:15.000 --> 14:16.710
Now that he's been taken away,

14:17.150 --> 14:19.080
the marriage was never completed.

14:19.080 --> 14:21.680
Surely you won't
make things difficult for me?

14:21.920 --> 14:22.610
If

14:22.970 --> 14:24.920
you're an ordinary citizen of Changmo,

14:24.920 --> 14:26.550
I won't make things difficult for you.

14:26.550 --> 14:27.670
But if you are not,

14:28.510 --> 14:30.110
then that's another matter.

14:58.270 --> 14:58.910
Here.

15:04.400 --> 15:05.400
What's your name?

15:06.320 --> 15:07.510
Everyone calls me

15:09.130 --> 15:10.010
Ling.

15:12.680 --> 15:14.540
Why did you want to marry Zhao Gao?

15:19.360 --> 15:20.200
I

15:20.630 --> 15:22.550
got lost in the desert

15:22.890 --> 15:24.350
and was saved by Lord Zhao.

15:24.750 --> 15:26.600
I promised to marry him

15:26.960 --> 15:28.220
to repay his kindness.

15:28.360 --> 15:29.290
Now that Zhao Gao

15:29.440 --> 15:30.500
has been arrested,

15:30.760 --> 15:32.020
why are you still here?

15:33.870 --> 15:35.470
Since I can't repay his kindness,

15:35.470 --> 15:36.870
I will return to Changmo.

15:37.460 --> 15:38.520
Is it worth making such a big sacrifice

15:38.520 --> 15:40.450
just to go to the capital?

15:40.920 --> 15:43.180
Han Mo is in Jinglan Capital's dungeons,

15:43.440 --> 15:44.790
and he is seriously ill.

15:45.000 --> 15:46.030
Without timely treatment,

15:46.030 --> 15:47.270
he may not survive.

15:47.840 --> 15:49.750
He is my uncle's only son

15:50.180 --> 15:52.280
and the only male heir of the Han family.

15:52.280 --> 15:54.480
Even if it costs my life, I must save him.

15:55.730 --> 15:57.000
Only by pretending to marry Zhao Gao

15:57.000 --> 15:59.060
can I have the chance to go to Jinglan.

15:59.080 --> 16:00.030
I can't fail now.

16:00.390 --> 16:01.510
I have to stay.

16:02.720 --> 16:03.550
Before I leave,

16:03.550 --> 16:05.370
I'd like to give you a piece of advice.

16:05.370 --> 16:07.680
Your old injury and hidden condition
need immediate treatment,

16:07.680 --> 16:09.560
or you won't live long.

16:09.750 --> 16:10.410
How dare you

16:10.610 --> 16:11.740
curse General Xiao!

16:12.440 --> 16:14.750
Have you suffered from
cold limbs and a weak body

16:14.750 --> 16:15.920
since childhood?

16:16.030 --> 16:17.390
How do you know that?

16:17.650 --> 16:19.560
I've studied medicine since I was young.

16:19.560 --> 16:21.210
Such obvious symptoms can be seen

16:21.210 --> 16:23.740
by anyone with
even basic medical knowledge.

16:24.530 --> 16:25.730
Don't talk nonsense.

16:25.820 --> 16:26.420
Tell me,

16:27.230 --> 16:28.490
what illness do I have?

16:30.200 --> 16:31.670
You have constipation.

16:33.120 --> 16:34.250
How can you tell?

16:35.240 --> 16:35.880
Well,

16:36.480 --> 16:37.480
can you treat him?

16:38.020 --> 16:38.660
Of course.

16:38.830 --> 16:40.190
Not only his condition—

16:40.360 --> 16:41.360
I can treat yours

16:41.550 --> 16:42.550
as well.

16:42.990 --> 16:43.990
Will you stay

16:44.450 --> 16:46.400
and treat both of us?

16:50.360 --> 16:52.080
If the medical fee is right,

16:52.330 --> 16:53.560
I have no objection.

16:54.840 --> 16:55.320
Okay.

16:56.250 --> 16:58.250
Then I'll leave it to you, Miss Ling.

16:59.170 --> 16:59.830
Chengfeng.

17:00.150 --> 17:00.750
Yes.

17:00.770 --> 17:02.430
Take her back to the residence

17:03.050 --> 17:04.440
and change her clothes.

17:05.069 --> 17:05.550
Okay.

17:09.369 --> 17:10.220
Well,

17:10.369 --> 17:11.819
Were you just

17:11.849 --> 17:13.160
making that up

17:13.430 --> 17:14.760
about my condition?

17:16.800 --> 17:18.220
Take me back to the General's residence.

17:18.220 --> 17:19.550
I promise I'll cure you.

17:21.380 --> 17:23.069
[General's Mansion]

17:27.630 --> 17:29.430
Does she really not remember me?

17:34.850 --> 17:36.050
This river is so deep.

17:36.310 --> 17:37.310
If you fall in,

17:37.380 --> 17:38.660
we'll both die.

17:39.100 --> 17:40.450
Why would you die?

17:40.710 --> 17:41.880
If you jump in,

17:42.350 --> 17:43.830
I can't just stand by and watch.

17:43.830 --> 17:44.680
But...

17:45.160 --> 17:46.270
I can't swim,

17:46.350 --> 17:48.750
so I'd end up drowning with you.

17:51.270 --> 17:53.510
Why did she suddenly show up here again?

17:55.560 --> 17:57.080
What's really going on?

18:03.070 --> 18:04.440
What repayment of kindness?

18:04.440 --> 18:05.070
I know

18:05.200 --> 18:06.960
you're a spy from Changmo.

18:07.950 --> 18:08.480
General,

18:08.500 --> 18:09.360
leave her to me.

18:09.400 --> 18:10.480
I'll interrogate her properly

18:10.480 --> 18:11.920
and find evidence.

18:13.610 --> 18:15.090
Xu Chengfeng.

18:26.160 --> 18:27.020
Lieutenant Xu.

18:27.990 --> 18:28.750
Miss Ling.

18:28.810 --> 18:30.310
Why are you still up so late?

18:30.310 --> 18:30.810
I'm waiting for you.

18:30.810 --> 18:31.670
Waiting for me?

18:34.250 --> 18:34.980
What is this?

18:35.190 --> 18:36.710
The pill inside is for you.

18:37.070 --> 18:39.310
It specifically treats constipation.

18:41.300 --> 18:41.760
Just...

18:41.840 --> 18:42.710
one pill?

18:42.860 --> 18:43.560
Will it really work?

18:43.560 --> 18:45.560
You'll know once you try it.

18:47.160 --> 18:48.360
And the paper inside

18:48.380 --> 18:50.010
is the prescription for General Xiao.

18:50.010 --> 18:52.010
You have one day to gather the herbs.

18:52.480 --> 18:53.410
Tomorrow night,

18:53.580 --> 18:54.840
I'll treat the General

18:54.940 --> 18:55.560
with acupuncture.

18:55.560 --> 18:57.220
It won't even take a whole day.

18:57.480 --> 18:59.310
General Xiao is deeply
loved by the people.

18:59.310 --> 19:00.510
If he needs medicine,

19:00.530 --> 19:02.480
the whole city will come to help.

19:04.400 --> 19:04.920
Okay.

19:05.250 --> 19:05.860
Remember,

19:06.130 --> 19:07.930
not a single herb can be missing.

19:10.170 --> 19:11.130
Let me tell you.

19:11.160 --> 19:12.050
Nothing about the General

19:12.050 --> 19:13.960
is beyond my ability.

19:16.790 --> 19:18.200
We're still missing a few herbs.

19:18.200 --> 19:21.350
Didn't you say your General is so loved

19:21.750 --> 19:23.440
that the whole city would help

19:23.530 --> 19:25.290
if it's for him?

19:25.320 --> 19:26.920
They did help—

19:27.200 --> 19:28.160
but some herbs

19:28.160 --> 19:29.180
only grow in the south.

19:29.180 --> 19:30.410
They don't exist at Tianlang Pass at all.

19:30.410 --> 19:31.210
Xu Chengfeng.

19:31.440 --> 19:33.880
You made the whole city
look for herbs for me?

19:33.880 --> 19:35.210
What were you thinking?

19:35.390 --> 19:35.850
General,

19:35.850 --> 19:36.310
I...

19:38.720 --> 19:40.330
Can... can these herbs

19:40.360 --> 19:41.970
treat the General's illness?

19:41.970 --> 19:42.650
Never mind.

19:42.850 --> 19:44.480
I'll use acupuncture for now.

19:44.480 --> 19:45.850
Once all the herbs are gathered,
I'll prepare the medicine.

19:45.850 --> 19:47.000
Alright, Dr. Ling.

19:47.030 --> 19:47.760
Then please…

19:49.790 --> 19:50.510
please treat...

19:50.510 --> 19:51.040
treat...

19:51.320 --> 19:52.190
the General.

19:54.720 --> 19:55.520
What's wrong?

19:56.120 --> 19:56.710
I'm fine.

19:56.890 --> 19:57.350
Please.

20:00.390 --> 20:01.990
Take your upper clothes off.

20:04.350 --> 20:05.600
I have to take my clothes off?

20:05.600 --> 20:06.360
Of course.

20:06.980 --> 20:09.710
How can I perform acupuncture
through clothing?

20:12.790 --> 20:13.380
General.

20:13.790 --> 20:15.200
Just take off your clothes.

20:15.200 --> 20:16.330
With me by your side,

20:16.680 --> 20:18.140
you won't be in any danger.

20:18.580 --> 20:19.860
What's wrong with you?

20:20.060 --> 20:20.510
I...

20:22.520 --> 20:24.320
It must be the medicine working.

20:24.730 --> 20:25.490
To be honest,

20:25.880 --> 20:26.410
General,

20:26.790 --> 20:27.750
I really can't

20:28.090 --> 20:29.160
hold it in anymore.

20:31.200 --> 20:32.130
Then go quickly.

20:32.830 --> 20:33.790
Yes, General.

20:33.960 --> 20:35.290
Wait for me to come back.

20:35.550 --> 20:37.240
Don't start the treatment yet.

20:37.240 --> 20:38.750
Should we wait for him?

20:40.580 --> 20:41.270
No need.

20:42.640 --> 20:44.570
Aren't you afraid I might harm you?

20:47.830 --> 20:49.360
If so, I'll return this life

20:49.400 --> 20:50.160
to you.

21:05.590 --> 21:07.050
Aren't you going to start?

21:07.270 --> 21:08.270
I'm starting now.

21:35.560 --> 21:37.400
What exactly happened to you?

21:37.780 --> 21:39.500
Maybe I can save you.

21:41.530 --> 21:42.260
Does it hurt?

21:42.420 --> 21:43.200
No.

21:45.600 --> 21:46.630
Then bear with

21:46.770 --> 21:47.900
this needle as well.

22:12.000 --> 22:12.480
Are you

22:14.360 --> 22:15.490
really called Ling?

22:16.720 --> 22:17.920
Why would I lie to you?

22:22.440 --> 22:22.990
Then,

22:23.750 --> 22:26.010
have you ever been to Jinglan's capital?

22:28.860 --> 22:29.580
No.

22:32.060 --> 22:32.780
If

22:34.490 --> 22:35.680
a child wanted to

22:36.110 --> 22:37.110
take his own life,

22:37.790 --> 22:38.850
would you save him?

22:40.490 --> 22:42.620
If he is determined to die,

22:43.000 --> 22:44.440
even if I save him once,

22:44.630 --> 22:45.800
he will try again.

22:46.440 --> 22:47.900
Then why should I save him?

22:51.850 --> 22:52.380
Alright.

22:52.920 --> 22:55.250
General, you can put your clothes back on.

23:01.110 --> 23:02.350
How do you feel?

23:04.750 --> 23:05.510
Much better.

23:06.550 --> 23:07.270
You won't doubt

23:07.270 --> 23:09.070
my medical skills now, will you?

23:11.570 --> 23:12.280
I never

23:12.790 --> 23:13.750
doubted them.

23:18.570 --> 23:20.850
I've never been to

23:20.870 --> 23:22.470
that capital you mentioned,

23:22.590 --> 23:24.400
but I'm sure Jinglan's capital

23:24.420 --> 23:26.350
must be very grand and prosperous.

23:26.750 --> 23:28.920
I would really like to see it.

23:31.480 --> 23:33.680
If the war between the two nations ends,

23:35.160 --> 23:36.880
I will definitely take you there.

23:36.880 --> 23:38.010
Then it's a promise.

23:39.310 --> 23:39.880
Okay.

23:46.480 --> 23:47.680
It's so late.

23:47.710 --> 23:49.510
Why isn't the General back yet?

23:50.430 --> 23:52.880
The whole Tianlang Pass
is under his command.

23:52.880 --> 23:55.080
He must have a lot to deal with every day.

23:56.460 --> 23:59.220
But I heard that since Dr. Ling arrived,

23:59.240 --> 24:01.500
the General's health has improved a lot.

24:01.710 --> 24:02.800
Yes.

24:05.500 --> 24:06.070
Ling.

24:06.320 --> 24:07.190
Dr. Ling.

24:07.770 --> 24:09.130
Where are you going?

24:12.340 --> 24:14.620
I couldn't sleep,
so I came out for a walk.

24:15.970 --> 24:16.820
Dr. Ling.

24:17.050 --> 24:18.250
It's already late.

24:18.370 --> 24:20.030
There's no one on the streets.

24:20.160 --> 24:21.270
Tianlang Pass may be peaceful

24:21.270 --> 24:23.430
and doors are not locked at night,

24:23.610 --> 24:25.610
but you are a girl after all.

24:26.700 --> 24:29.420
General Xiao still
hasn't returned so late.

24:29.520 --> 24:31.330
It's time for his treatment.

24:31.700 --> 24:33.700
If his condition suddenly worsens,

24:33.920 --> 24:35.400
that'll be serious.

24:35.980 --> 24:36.980
I see.

24:37.350 --> 24:38.550
Then you should go quickly.

24:38.550 --> 24:40.160
Don't delay the General's treatment.

24:40.160 --> 24:41.000
Okay, okay.

24:48.510 --> 24:49.370
I'll treat him.

24:50.270 --> 24:51.310
Tr- Treat him.

25:03.270 --> 25:03.920
Ms. Wu.

25:04.200 --> 25:06.590
You are quite familiar with Tianlang Pass.

25:06.590 --> 25:08.270
Can you help me think of a way

25:08.290 --> 25:09.960
to get out of the pass
as soon as possible?

25:09.960 --> 25:10.920
Tianlang Pass

25:10.920 --> 25:13.200
is nestled between two high mountains
to the north and south.

25:13.200 --> 25:14.590
Changmo lies to the west,

25:14.590 --> 25:15.910
and Jinglan to the east.

25:15.910 --> 25:17.990
There's a checkpoint in the middle—

25:18.190 --> 25:20.670
that's the real obstacle.

25:20.940 --> 25:22.400
Without Xiao Chi's pass token,

25:22.400 --> 25:24.070
no one is allowed through.

25:24.240 --> 25:25.310
Why?

25:25.450 --> 25:26.570
I heard that years ago,

25:26.570 --> 25:28.510
Changmo sent several batches
of spies to Jinglan.

25:28.510 --> 25:30.030
After Xiao Chi became a general,

25:30.030 --> 25:31.200
he rebuilt the checkpoints

25:31.200 --> 25:32.590
and introduced pass tokens,

25:32.590 --> 25:34.850
making it extremely difficult to cross.

25:35.180 --> 25:36.200
What should I do then?

25:36.200 --> 25:38.110
I must go to Jinglan as soon as possible.

25:38.110 --> 25:39.200
Why don't you go find Zhao Gao?

25:39.200 --> 25:40.400
Maybe he has a way.

25:40.820 --> 25:43.060
Wasn't Zhao Gao captured by Xiao Chi?

25:44.400 --> 25:45.690
He is an envoy after all.

25:45.690 --> 25:47.940
He must have a special pass token.

25:48.960 --> 25:51.160
Then I can only try my luck at the prison.

25:58.790 --> 26:00.030
Fire!

26:00.050 --> 26:01.000
Fire!

26:01.110 --> 26:02.200
Someone help!

26:02.200 --> 26:03.000
Go get some water!

26:03.000 --> 26:03.720
Put the fire out!

26:03.720 --> 26:05.000
What should we do?

26:05.000 --> 26:06.030
Fire!

26:06.230 --> 26:06.920
Hurry up!

26:06.960 --> 26:07.830
Come over here!

26:07.830 --> 26:09.590
How could this happen?

26:09.620 --> 26:10.790
The residence is completely burned down.

26:10.790 --> 26:13.160
How will I explain this to the envoy?

26:14.230 --> 26:15.040
How did

26:15.400 --> 26:16.530
the fire even start?

26:16.630 --> 26:17.710
I don't know.

26:17.870 --> 26:19.590
By the time I found out,

26:19.610 --> 26:21.040
it was already out of control.

26:21.040 --> 26:21.680
General.

26:21.750 --> 26:22.550
He is right.

26:22.550 --> 26:23.170
I've questioned

26:23.170 --> 26:25.260
all the remaining servants
in the residence.

26:25.260 --> 26:26.260
No one was on duty

26:26.430 --> 26:27.840
when the fire started.

26:28.400 --> 26:28.930
General.

26:29.050 --> 26:30.950
We just arrested Zhao Gao,

26:31.070 --> 26:32.830
and now the envoy's residence is on fire.

26:32.830 --> 26:34.630
This is definitely suspicious.

26:38.690 --> 26:39.960
What should we do?

26:50.610 --> 26:51.940
The fire likely started

26:52.640 --> 26:54.130
in the northwest corner first.

26:54.130 --> 26:56.730
And northwest winds are common
in this season.

26:56.760 --> 26:57.630
Whoever set it

26:57.880 --> 26:59.200
clearly knew that.

26:59.840 --> 27:02.160
Being able to get onto
the roof without a ladder,

27:02.160 --> 27:04.090
this person must be quite capable.

27:05.400 --> 27:07.400
No ordinary civilian could do this—

27:08.080 --> 27:09.410
it must be one of our own.

27:13.350 --> 27:16.280
[Prison]

27:46.640 --> 27:48.440
Who's breaking into the prison?

27:49.910 --> 27:50.640
Who's there?

27:53.960 --> 27:54.810
Dr. Ling.

27:55.270 --> 27:56.200
Why are you here?

27:56.400 --> 27:57.700
A few days ago outside the city gate,

27:57.700 --> 27:59.900
you saved my son from the brink of death.

27:59.900 --> 28:00.690
Dr. Ling.

28:00.810 --> 28:02.290
Thank you so much.

28:04.350 --> 28:05.980
What brings you

28:06.110 --> 28:07.310
to the prison so late?

28:07.790 --> 28:09.550
I came specifically to find you.

28:09.550 --> 28:10.310
Find me?

28:10.750 --> 28:12.380
Today I read some medical texts

28:12.380 --> 28:13.410
and found several herbs

28:13.410 --> 28:16.010
that could greatly
help your son's condition.

28:16.550 --> 28:17.550
Dr. Ling.

28:17.830 --> 28:19.550
You've been so kind to me.

28:20.000 --> 28:20.720
Please,

28:21.750 --> 28:23.640
tell me—I'll remember everything.

28:23.640 --> 28:25.240
There are quite a few of them.

28:25.310 --> 28:26.510
I'm afraid you won't remember them all.

28:26.510 --> 28:27.240
Why don't you

28:27.360 --> 28:28.920
get some paper and ink?

28:29.110 --> 28:30.540
I'll write them down for you.

28:30.540 --> 28:32.020
Thank you so much.

28:34.490 --> 28:34.900
Come.

28:37.030 --> 28:37.630
Thank you.

28:37.900 --> 28:39.060
Thank you, Dr. Ling.

28:40.520 --> 28:41.600
No need to thank me.

28:47.030 --> 28:48.850
You didn't come to the prison this late

28:48.850 --> 28:51.050
just to hand me a prescription, did you?

28:53.400 --> 28:54.790
I'll tell you the truth.

28:55.020 --> 28:56.880
I'm actually here to see Zhao Gao.

28:57.200 --> 28:57.960
Zhao Gao?

29:00.270 --> 29:01.670
Why do you want to see him?

29:02.000 --> 29:02.960
As you know,

29:03.360 --> 29:05.880
Zhao Gao may be bad,
but he did me a favor.

29:06.400 --> 29:07.400
I want to see him

29:07.580 --> 29:08.910
and thank him in person.

29:10.400 --> 29:11.900
To repay kindness with gratitude…

29:11.900 --> 29:14.300
Dr. Ling, you are
truly a righteous person.

29:15.170 --> 29:15.780
Well.

29:15.970 --> 29:18.300
I am also someone who repays kindness.

29:18.510 --> 29:19.640
I'll help you.

29:20.400 --> 29:22.590
Zhao Gao is in the last cell.

29:22.610 --> 29:23.470
Go by yourself.

29:23.770 --> 29:24.400
Thank you.

29:37.920 --> 29:38.670
Zhao Gao.

29:42.090 --> 29:42.770
Wait.

29:43.110 --> 29:44.310
Why is it you?

29:44.900 --> 29:46.010
How did you get in?

29:46.170 --> 29:47.400
That's not important.

29:47.400 --> 29:48.260
I just want to ask you,

29:48.260 --> 29:49.790
do you want to get out or not?

29:50.880 --> 29:52.350
You can get me out?

29:52.440 --> 29:53.720
Who exactly are you?

29:53.930 --> 29:54.380
Wait.

29:54.460 --> 29:55.380
Whoever you are,

29:55.380 --> 29:56.620
if you can get me out,

29:56.880 --> 29:58.340
gold, jewels, land deeds—

29:58.340 --> 29:59.650
anything you want, I'll give it to you.

29:59.650 --> 30:01.650
I am not interested in any of that.

30:01.790 --> 30:03.590
Then what are you interested in?

30:03.720 --> 30:04.680
I want to know

30:04.950 --> 30:06.110
whether the Envoy's token

30:06.110 --> 30:08.020
can pass the checkpoint at Tianlang Pass.

30:08.020 --> 30:08.700
Of course.

30:08.790 --> 30:09.720
I am the Empress Dowager's brother,

30:09.720 --> 30:11.150
an imperial envoy
appointed by His Majesty.

30:11.150 --> 30:12.750
Who would dare stop my token?

30:13.350 --> 30:14.830
If someone else took that token,

30:14.830 --> 30:15.770
could they still pass?

30:15.770 --> 30:18.330
Those soldiers only recognize
the token, not the person.

30:18.330 --> 30:19.180
Where is the token?

30:19.180 --> 30:20.830
My token is...

30:28.640 --> 30:30.510
as long as you get me out of here,

30:31.070 --> 30:33.200
I will give it to you.

30:37.400 --> 30:39.400
Fine. It's a deal.

30:39.470 --> 30:40.710
It's a deal.

30:41.430 --> 30:42.470
General Xiao.

30:43.300 --> 30:44.130
General Xiao.

30:44.160 --> 30:46.220
What brings you here so late at night?

30:52.250 --> 30:54.380
Is there something urgent?

30:54.410 --> 30:55.900
Which cell is Zhao Gao in?

30:56.330 --> 30:57.530
The inner one.

30:57.560 --> 30:58.080
Got it.

30:58.280 --> 30:59.410
No need to follow me.

31:32.350 --> 31:33.260
Miss Ling?
